# AI Automation Lab

AI Automation Lab is a personal project space for building and testing AI-powered automation systems.

This repository focuses on practical AI workflows for content creation, custom websites, web automation, and revenue-focused digital projects.

## Key Goals

- Build AI-assisted content creation workflows
- Automate repetitive web and blog tasks
- Test AI tools for custom website production
- Improve productivity for digital business operations
- Develop reusable prompts, templates, and automation structures

## Project Areas

- Content automation
- Web automation
- AI workflow design
- Revenue-focused web systems

